Invocation Name: glyco pathway
des: Glyco Pathway describes each step of the glycolysis pathway in biology. The 10 steps of the glycolysis pathway are part of respiration in every living thing, breaking glucose down into pyruvate. Afterwards the pyruvate is further broken down and its energy extracted into ATP molecules, which power many of the operations inside living cells.
